# Cloudflare Pages _redirects
#
# These rules run at the CDN edge before any asset is served.
#
# Rule 1 & 2: Proxy /gateway/* and /health to the Cloudflare Worker so the
# frontend can use relative URLs in production (matching how the Vite dev
# proxy is configured in vite.config.ts).
#
# IMPORTANT: Replace the target origin below with your actual Worker URL if it
# differs from the default. The VITE_API_BASE_URL env var is for JS-level
# fetches; these rules handle the network-layer routing independently.
#
# Rule 3: SPA fallback — serve index.html for all other paths so client-side
# routing (wouter) works on hard reload or direct URL access.

/gateway/*  https://zamproject-api.zamdonations.workers.dev/gateway/:splat  200
/health     https://zamproject-api.zamdonations.workers.dev/health          200
/*          /index.html                                                      200
